      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SONNY (7) has been in the minor money at both career runs, the latest finishing second (26.30) at this track. Tough to beat if runs up to recent form. BRADMORE (4) jumped from box 1 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 11 lengths at this track in a handy 25.86. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Should feature again. GOODNIGHT JASPER (5) has finished in the placings both career runs so far, the latest when third (26.42) at this track. Has the ability and can measure up. PIECE OF ME (1) continues to race well and is sure to be competitive again.",
